<br />
This is the result of 100 coloured umbrellas, 50-100 cold and wet call centre staff, 7 crew, 2 cameras and one 27M cherry picker over 3 days.<br />
<br />
With the use of tilt-shift photography, the story follows people's unique outlet to everyday life, whilst a clown left behind in the excitement, drastically tries to join the fun.<br />
<br />
All shot in and around Portsmouth. With many thanks to Portsmouth City Council<br />
<br />
Music by Matthew and Me<br />
